# private folder is a SEPARATE repo (bitrix.infra-private) checked out at /private.
# Hard-exclude the whole dir so its contents (and its own .gitignore !-rules) can
# never show as untracked or be accidentally committed here. Already-tracked
# *.env.example / phpstan templates stay tracked (gitignore does not untrack).
/private/

